 je eigenständige Versuche frühjüdischer Identitätsbildung in der Zeit zwischen dem 4. Jh. v. Chr. und dem ausgehenden 1. Jh. n. Chr. sowie teils darüber hinaus. Insbesondere im Blick auf die altlateinische Version des Estherbuches, die hier erstmals in deutscher Übersetzung veröffentlicht ist, leistet die Studie einen gewichtigen Beitrag zur Forschung.  aThis monograph discusses the question of political theology with regard to the ancient Hebrew, Greek, and Latin versions of the Esther story. Each of the five versions appears as a separate attempt at early Jewish identity formation in the period between the 4th century BCE and the end of the 1st century CE. This study makes a major contribution to scholarship, especially with regard to the Old Latin version of the Book of Esther, published in an appendix for the first time in German translation.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aEster. 4aEsther. 4aPolitische Theologie. 4aSeptuaginta. 4aVetus Latina. 7aRELIGION / Ancient.2bisacsh  aEsther.  aSeptuagint.  aSeptuaginta.  aVetus Latina.  apolitical theology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theol., Relig.Stud., Jewish Stud. 2020z9783110704570oZDB-23-DGF0 cEPUBz97831106745520 cprintz978311067446040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311067451440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110674514423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110674514.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020